  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• This is a theoretical paper, presenting a comprehensive analysis of the skin effect in superconductors. This work is based solely on Newton and Maxwell's equations. Both the usual and anomalous skin effect are dealt with within a single framework. This enables us to validate an assumption widely used in the experiments.</subfield>
